{"tid":2496412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那狗譚德塞：全球有辦法在數月間控制疫情","createTime":"2021-04-19T22:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T23:14:34.000Z","uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cc13517a8eecbb572561acc07466a52d0acd3aa7","tid":2496412,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T22:11:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">譚德塞：全球有辦法在數月間控制疫情</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2021/04/20 01:17<br />\n<br />\n（中央社日內瓦19日綜合外電報導）世界衛生組織（WHO）秘書長譚德塞今天表示，全世界有辦法在未來數月間控制2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID－19）大流行疫情；他並敦促，公平分享全球資源。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）說：「我們有辦法在數月間控制這個大流行疫情，只要我們一貫而公平地使用這些辦法。」<br />\n<br />\n然而他也對疫情以「驚人速度」在世界各地25－59 歲人群中擴散，表示憂心。這可能是傳染性高出許多的變種病毒使然。<br />\n<br />\n世衛主要流行病學家范科霍芙（Maria van Kerkhove）說，「我們發現，疫情在所有年齡層的傳播速度已增加」；並說，上週全世界通報了520萬起新增病例，為疫情爆發以來的單週最多病例數。（譯者：張佑之）1100420"},{"pid":"0e8cd79b03e4d3f44b05b9702cafa74539fc6cd5","tid":2496412,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T22:13:03.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路"},{"pid":"840719be49f35ceb20ec44f5c5c03ee763b67853","tid":2496412,"uid":108078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T22:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />強制打4兄"},{"pid":"02cd48a037e68cd5101748f51dc1d8f355a52597","tid":2496412,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"840719be49f35ceb20ec44f5c5c03ee763b67853","tid":2496412,"uid":108078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T22:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />強制打4兄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T22:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支那疫苗"},{"pid":"16300591e62cf83909384038e76d5f750ff60b1e","tid":2496412,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T22:17:58.000Z","msg":"歡迎五毛跟帖"},{"pid":"b0027ad812843ef29f0268f16733b56e0290220f","tid":2496412,"uid"